        },
        "Represents a media file which can be added to a text message",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**accountId**: ~",
            "**created**: The time when the given resource was created, formatted in unix time milliseconds (read only). Example: 1473781817000 ",
            "**id**: An id of a media file",
            "**lengthInBytes**: A size of a media file in bytes",
            "**mediaType**: A MIME type of media file, ex: image/jpeg, image/png, video/mp4, audio/mp3, etc",
            "**name**: A name of a media file",
            "**publicUrl**: A public URL of a media file"
          ]
        },
        {
